prompt.title: Embedding for Promptbook:  Packages & Docker
prompt.content: The Promptbook engine is available as multiple npm packages and a Docker image.  Key packages include `ptbk` (all-in-one bundle), `@promptbook/core`, `@promptbook/utils`, and `@promptbook/cli`.  Specific LLM integrations are provided as separate packages (`@promptbook/openai`, `@promptbook/anthropic-claude`, etc.).
